既來之，則安之.pinyin: jì lái zhī ， zé ān zhī
既來之，則安之.definition: Since they have come, we should make them comfortable (idiom). Since we're here, take it easy.; Since this is so, we should accept it.; Now we have come, let's stay and take the rough with the smooth.; If you can't do anything to prevent it, you might as well sit back and enjoy it.

既往不咎.definition: to forget and not bear recriminations (idiom); to let bygones be bygones; There is no point in crying over spilt milk.

既是.definition: is both ...(and...); since; as; being the case that

既有今日何必當初.pinyin: jì yǒu jīn rì hé bì dāng chū
既有今日何必當初.definition: see 早知今日何必當初|早知今日何必当初[zao3 zhi1 jin1 ri4 he2 bi4 dang1 chu1]

既然.definition: since; as; this being the case

既要當婊子又要立牌坊.pinyin: jì yào dāng biǎo zi yòu yào lì pái fāng
既要當婊子又要立牌坊.definition: see 又想當婊子又想立牌坊|又想当婊子又想立牌坊[you4 xiang3 dang1 biao3 zi5 you4 xiang3 li4 pai2 fang1]
